{"version":"0.4","title":"facilities","type":"page","content":[{"id":"6468a35c","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"11e9724b","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"72086671","settings":{"title":"LIBRARY SYSTEM"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"8ecd6ae","settings":{"structure":"20"},"elements":[{"id":"f4a67e7","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"3fabbdcb","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/library-1.jpg","id":156}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"image","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"},{"id":"5fe14481","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"23b16aba","settings":{"editor":"<ul><li><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">BPIT offers a well-planned, centrally air-conditioned library.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">BPIT library is well catered by for all the courses offered by the Institute.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">There are more than 45000+ books on all the subject fields.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.5; display: flex;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">Library system also offers ICT based resources to its uses, such as e-book, e-journals, and databases.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">A good number of thesis\/dissertations and research reports are available in library.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">Besides books, library system also possesses rare book collection, special reports, reference sources, audio-visual material etc.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">Library system uses LIBWARE 3.0.3 for handling day to day routine tasks. It makes use of RFID and Barcode system for inventory and security of library materials.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; stroke: #3f3f3f;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif;\">A good number of International and National Journals \u2013 55 (IEEE Journals, IETE, etc.)<\/span><\/span><\/li><\/ul>","text_color":"#220DE9"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"12cc290","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"70467976","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"7f1591a7","settings":{"title":"GIRL'S HOSTEL"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"1ea80de9","settings":{"structure":"20"},"elements":[{"id":"134dce70","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"62f53edb","settings":{"carousel":[{"id":161,"url":"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hostel1.jpg"},{"id":162,"url":"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hostel2.jpg"},{"id":163,"url":"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hostel3.jpg"}],"thumbnail_size":"2048x2048","slides_to_show":"1","image_stretch":"yes","arrows_size":{"unit":"px","size":21,"sizes":[]},"dots_position":"inside","image_border_border":"solid","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"-1","right":"-1","bottom":"-1","left":"-1","isLinked":true},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true},"_element_vertical_align":"center","_position":"absolute"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"image-carousel","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"},{"id":"227a1dc","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"2111ed25","settings":{"editor":"<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: #220de9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">The hostel is \u2018A home away from home\u2019 for girls coming from all parts of the country. BPIT offers well furnished hostel facilities within the college campus.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">The hostel was founded in the year 2011 and was inaugurated by Shri P.K. Tripathi , Chief Secretary, Delhi Government. The hostel provides all the resident students a safe and comfortable environment and is a Zero ragging zone.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">For operational convenience, the hostel has Dr. Muskan Kapoor as Hostel-In Charge and 2 Wardens. Caring wardens, vigilant security and cleaning staff ensures a pleasant stay allowing students to focus on academics.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">Hostel has capacity of 64 twin sharing rooms to accommodate 128 girls and a full time Mess serving a fairly varied menu of absolutely fresh food, while giving considerable attention to its nutritive value to the residents. Hostel has a separate Girls Common Room, Washing area with a washing Machine, Kitchen with all necessary facilities. College and hostel authorities make sure to conduct regular visits and surveys in order to undertake repairs and maintenance accordingly.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">Taking ahead the good practices &amp; initiatives, the Management of BPIT has installed Solar Power Plant on the rooftop of Girls Hostel for generation of 37.68 KW power by non-conventional method. The Management plans to install solar power plants on the rooftops of other part of the Institute with the sole aim to become self reliant.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\"><\/p>","text_color":"#6EC1E4","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Roboto","typography_font_weight":"400","__globals__":{"text_color":""}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"73aedd99","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"22702b32","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"7ae0df71","settings":{"title":"OUR CANTEEN"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"19f02e60","settings":{"structure":"20"},"elements":[{"id":"3700a56e","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"3bd94b31","settings":{"image":{"url":"http:\/\/127.0.0.1\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/canteen_img.jpg","id":168}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"image","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"},{"id":"317d07f3","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"5489f5d8","settings":{"editor":"<h6 style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0BPIT has a spacious canteen which maintains strict hygienic and sanitary conditions and serves quality meals, snacks and beverages at concessional rates. The canteen is located at a central place in the campus from where all the facilities can be served to the faculty members within a reasonable time. The Institute has an intercom facility and the canteen is also well-connected with all the rooms through the same. There is a separate seating space for faculty and staff members having a capacity of 20 members whereas the seating capacity of the area reserved for students is around 60 students.<\/h6>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">The canteen serves Indian, South Indian, Chinese and continental snack items. There are refrigerators, micro wave oven, coffee machine and tea machines for serving the food\/beverage items at appropriate temperature as desired.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">On the demand of students &amp; in order to supplement the canteen services, the Management has opened two outlets. One such outlet provides Hot &amp; Cold Coffee with other eatables &amp; and another provides Ice-creams, Milk, Lassi, cold drinks etc.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #220DE9; line-height: 2rem; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\">The students enjoy, relax and refresh themselves in the canteen during the breaks. There is adequate and amenable staff in the canteen who provide quick and quality service to the students and faculty members.<\/p>","text_color":"#120EC3"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"22cd7ad2","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"7618f284","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"4b280fc4","settings":{"title":"Sports Facilities\u200b"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"749acb8a","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"1283e295","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"3c2a27c2","settings":{"editor":"<span style=\"color: #120EC3; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Sports Program at Bhagwan Parshuram Institute of Technology is designed to serve student interest in different sports and recreational activities. These interests can be competitive, recreational or instructional in nature; students may represent the College in inter-university competition or intra-branch league activities such as tournament play, training, instruction, and social interaction (recreational) events. Keeping this in view, the institute has invested heavily in creating good sports infrastructure. Following are the facilities provided in sports at BPIT:<\/span>","text_color":"#120EC3"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"},{"id":"277854ca","settings":{"structure":"20"},"elements":[{"id":"3e931b72","settings":{"_column_size":50,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"1e6dd9d9","settings":{"title":"Outdoor Activities<br><br><br>"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"},{"id":"12e5011","settings":{"structure":"20"},"elements":[{"id":"10d0d6